Fun Fact: Their "mermaid pouches" can be found on beaches across the world!
Most Distinctive Feature: Flat body type that's similar to stringrays
Gestation Period: Eggs take 3 to 5 months to hatch depending on species
Habitat: Generally found in along continental shelfs
Origin: Believed to have first evolved in the Jurassic Period (200 to 145 million years ago)
Name: Skate Fish
